(127, 2, 'Which situation is consistent with the law of diminishing marginal utility?', 'The more pizza Henry eats, the more he enjoys another slice.', 0, 'The more pizza Henry eats, the less he enjoys another slice.', 1, 'Henry''s marginal utility from eating pizza becomes positive after eating three\r\nslices.', 0, 'Henry''s marginal utility from eating pizza reaches a maximum when total utility\r\nis zero.', 0, 'None of the above', 0, 'The more pizza Henry eats, the less he enjoys another slice.', NULL, NULL),
